rnoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20this%20point%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20had%20previously%20underestimated%20Research%20Triangle%20Park's%20homebuying%20competitiveness%20the%20first%20time.%20The%20area%20is%20in%20high%20demand%2C%20so%20I%20came%20in%20strong%2C%20offering%20about%20%2450%2C000%20over%20asking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20we%20ended%20up%20losing%20the%20house.%20It%20sold%20after%20just%20one%20open%20house.%20There%20were%20lines%20of%20parked%20cars%20around%20the%20block%20to%20see%20this%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ordeal%20made%20my%20family%20cry.%20I%20can%20laugh%20about%20it%20now%2C%20but%20the%20reality%20is%2C%20I%20look%20at%20this%20data%20all%20the%20time.%20According%20to%20Zillow's%20Consumer%20Housing%20Trends%20Report%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20buyers%20cry%20at%20least%20once%20during%20the%20homebuying%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20deeply%20familiar%20with%20everything%20we%20know%20at%20Zillow%20about%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20of%20shopping%20for%20a%20home%2C%20but%20I%20still%20didn't%20think%20it%20would%20happen%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a0db9b6-9971-4696-9dae-ace9bcc515c9%5C%22%3EThe%20third%20time%20was%20the%20charm%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I%20had%20to%20fly%20back%20to%20Seattle%2C%20so%20I%20began%20relying%20entirely%20on%20my%20agent%2C%20who%20was%20much%20more%20familiar%20with%20the%20area.%20I%20also%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-association-realtors-rules-commissions-zillow-home-search-pocket-listings-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EZillow%3C%2Fa%3E%20alerts%20set%20up%20for%20my%20preferred%20neighborhood%20and%20checked%20them%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20my%20agent%20got%20a%20call%20from%20another%20agent%20who%20said%20she%20knew%20of%20a%20homeowner%20who%20may%20be%20willing%20to%20sell%20if%20we%20agreed%20to%20all%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20saw%20photos%20of%20the%20house%20%E2%80%94%20it%2