tered%20by%20Russia's%20advanced%20air%20defense%20systems%2C%20like%20its%20S-300%20and%20S-400%20missile%20launchers.%20But%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20these%20latest%20drones%20didn't%20need%20to%20run%20the%20S-400%20gauntlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20flying%20larger%2C%20long-range%20drones%20through%20Russian%20airspace%20from%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20SBU%20said%20they%20trucked%20the%20containers%20out%20to%20the%20airfields%2C%20activating%20the%20smuggled%20drones%20after%20remotely%20retracting%20the%20roofs%20to%20release%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20much-shortened%20and%20simplified%20journey%20to%20their%20target%2C%20the%20drones%20struck%20warplanes%20at%20the%20airfields%20of%20Belaya%2C%20Diaghilev%2C%20Olenya%2C%20and%20Ivanovo%2C%20per%20the%20SBU.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2233fff348-af03-458c-8165-689c5b36a63e%5C%22%3EA%20powerful%20statement%20of%20Ukraine%20going%20it%20alone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELithuania's%20former%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Gabrelius%20Landsbergis%2C%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20attack%20shows%20Ukraine's%20ability%20to%20innovate%20and%20surprise%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIts%20scale%20and%20ingenuity%20%E2%80%94%20carried%20out%20without%20visible%20Western%20intelligence%20or%20logistical%20support%20%E2%80%94%20suggests%20Ukraine%20is%20now%20less%20reliant%20on%20outside%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flandsbergis.com%2Fthe-security-guarantees-europe-needs-are-being-made-in-ukraine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Ukraine's%20Western%20backers%2C%20like%20the%20US%2C%20have%20resisted%20providing%20the%20weaponry%20and%20intelligence%20Ukraine%20has%20sought%20for%20retaliation%20against%20Russian%20bases%2C%20from%20which%20it%20launches%20regular%20attacks%20on%20Ukrainian%20civilian%20infrastructure%20and%20defensive%20lines.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowered%20largely%20by%20domestically-produced%20armaments%2C%20Ukraine%20once%20again%20innovated%20%26quot%3Bwhile%20the%20world%20talks%2C%20hosts%20meetings%2C%20and%20forms%20yet%20another%20'coalition%20of%20the%20willing%2C'%26quot%3B%20Landsbergis%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUkraine%20is%20preparing%20to%20fight%20on%20its%20own%20terms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20ever%20wondered%20what%20strategic%20autonomy%20looks%20like%20%E2%80%94%20this%20might%20be%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20showed%20that%20its%20fleet%20of%20%24150%20million%20bombers%20on%20a%20runway%20can%20be%20made%20prey%20to%20the%20kind%20of%20cheap%20drones%20modified%20slightly%20from%20racing%20and%20wedding%20photos.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c840b76d-2685-4ae9-a7d0-69c5116d01a0%5C%22%3EIt%20enables%20Ukraine%20to%20hit%20deeper%20into%20Russia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20these%20coordinated%20strikes%2C%20Ukraine's%20drone%20attacks%20on%20Russia%20have%20reached%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kyivpost.com%2Fpost%2F33333%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20far%20as%201%2C100%20miles%20from%20their%20shared%20border%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20distance%20is%20dwarfed%20by%20the%20reach%20of%20Sunday's%20attack%2C%20where%20the%20farthest%20airfield%2C%20at%20Belaya%20in%20the%20eastern-central%20Irkutsk%20region%2C%20was%20more%20than%202%2C500%20miles%20from%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20likely%20viewed%20bases%20far%20from%20Ukraine%20as%20being%20at%20less%20risk%20of%20attack.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBronk%20said%20that%20even%20if%20only%20half%20of%20the%20claimed%2041%20planes%20were%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%2C%20it%20would%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20impact%26quot%3B%20on%20Russia's%20ability%20to%20launch%20long-range%20cruise%20missile%20attacks%20on%20Ukraine's%20civilian%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBronk%20estimates%20that%20Russia%20had%20around%2060%20active%20Tu-95%20%26quot%3BBear%26quot%3B%20bombers%20and%20around%2020%20Tu-160%20%26quot%3BBlackjack