0she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20when%20we%20get%20the%20most%20creative%20ideas%20and%20uses%20of%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222670%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alicia%20Morrison%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6838b5d9c6ad288d14822d5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222003%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlicia%20Morrison%20is%20the%20director%20of%20data%20science%20at%20Mercy%20Corps.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Cloudera%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227bff8e2e-4219-4a8e-8a04-44fe36d073fc%5C%22%3EKey%20staff%20and%20partners%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMercy%20Corps%20took%20part%20in%20Tech%20To%20the%20Rescue's%20AI%20for%20Changemakers%20program%2C%20a%20global%20accelerator%20that%20helps%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbridges-to-prosperity-nonprofit-ai-mapping-waterways-rural-communities-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enonprofits%3C%2Fa%3E%20experiment%20with%20AI.%20Through%20intensive%2C%20short-term%20training%20programs%2C%20Tech%20To%20the%20Rescue%20gives%20organizations%20a%20chance%20to%20pitch%20AI%20ideas%20and%20connect%20with%20private%20sector%20partners%20who%20can%20help%20bring%20them%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMercy%20Corps%20matched%20with%20Cloudera%2C%20a%20software%20company%20focused%20on%20data%20management%2C%20analytics%2C%20and%20AI.%20%26quot%3BThey%20had%20the%20idea%20and%20we%20believed%20we%20could%20contribute%20our%20time%2C%20resources%2C%20and%20skills%20and%20add%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rob%20Dickens%2C%20a%20solutions%20architect%20at%20Cloudera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECloudera%20donated%20engineering%20time%20and%20platform%20credits%20to%20develop%20the%20product%2C%20which%20is%20called%20the%20AI%20Methods%20Matcher.%20Dickens%20said%20development%20took%20about%20seven%20weeks%2C%20and%20the%20tool%20runs%20on%20Cloudera's%20AI%20Inference%20service%2C%20which%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272552ab7-00d1-45b1-8ae9-e20ab5f042c9%5C%22%3EAI%20in%20action%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMethods%20Matcher%20uses%20a%20type%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-evolution-software-companies-develop-ai-agents-workforce-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretrieval-augmented-generation-making-ai-language-models-better-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretrieval-augmented%20generation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20draws%20on%20an%20archive%20of%20successful%20projects%20to%20search%20for%20relevant%20information%2C%20summarize%20it%2C%20and%20offer%20recommendations.%20Now%2C%20decisions%20that%20aid%20workers%20make%20on%20the%20ground%20%E2%80%94%20from%20calculating%20vegetation%20health%20to%20tracking%20fertilizer%20distribution%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20guided%20by%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorrison%20said%20the%20tool%20speeds%20up%20decision-making%20by%20reducing%20the%20time%20and%20manual%20research%20required%20to%20analyze%20large%20volumes%20of%20information.%20With%20Methods%20Matcher%2C%20Mercy%20Corps'%20teams%20can%20identify%20actions%20that%20have%20worked%20elsewhere%20and%20get%20evidence-based%20suggestions%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20countries%20facing%20severe%20inflation%2C%20Mercy%20Corps%20often%20provides%20multipurpose%20cash%20assistance.%20But%20the%20organization%20needs%20to%20know%20the%20purchasing%20power%20of%20that%20cash%20to%20make%20an%20impact.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20an%20aid%20worker%20in%20the%20field%20might%20ask%20the%20tool%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20I%20determine%20how%20much%20cash%20aid%20to%20give%20people%20in%20a%20region%20with%20rising%20inflation%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMethods%20Matcher%20responds%20with%20a%20tailored%20answer%20based%20on%20past%20Mercy%20Corps%20projects%20and%20research.%20Aid%20workers%20can%20ask%20follow-up%20questions%20in%20the%20same%20session%2C%20and%20because%20the%20tool%20%26quot%3Bremembers%26quot%3B%20the%20conversation%20history%2C%20they%20can%20build%20on%20earlier%20questions%20without%20having%20to%20start%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20helps%20teams%20in%20the%20field%20quickly%20access%20information%20without%20waiting%20for%20support%20from%20HQ.%20%26quot%3BThey%20can%20see%20for%20themselves%20how%20valuable%20this%20kind%20of%20information%20can%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Morrison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rob%20Dickens%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6838b64cca50259add4d4f7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERob%20Dickens%20is%20a%20solutions%20architect%20at%20Cloudera.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Cloudera%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e42723e-1fcc-46c8-abee-483da1f34f81%5C%22%3EDid%20it%20work%2C%20and%20how%20did%20leaders%20know%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20tool's%20launch%20in%20November%202024%2C%20Morrison%20said%20that%20while%20they%20have%20yet%20to%20report%20metrics%20on%20the%20tool's%20impact%2C%20there%20has%20been%20strong%20early%20adoption%20among%20field%20teams.%20Mercy%20Corps%20is%20now%20working%20with%20Cloudera%20to%20expand%20Methods%20Matcher%2C%20develop%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexperiment-with-ai-tools-to-upskill-employees-says-google-researcher-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20build%20data%20literacy%20across%20the%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20gathering%20feedback%20on%20Methods%20Matcher%20from%20staff%20to%20understand%20what's%20working%20and%20what%20needs%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20a%