saved%20money%20and%20it%20left%20the%20community%20with%20new%20skills.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20hands-on%20approach%20not%20only%20reduced%20cost%20but%20also%20instilled%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%20among%20the%20locals.%20Even%20the%20students%20contributed%20through%3Cem%3E%20shramdaan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(voluntary%20work)%2C%20which%20added%20to%20the%20spirit%20of%20collective%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20pride%20in%20where%20they%20learn%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202023%2C%20Phase%201%20of%20Saraswati%20Vidyalaya%E2%80%99s%20transformation%20was%20complete.%20What%20now%20stands%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Tansa%20River%20is%20not%20only%20a%20structurally%20resilient%20school%2C%20it%20is%20a%20space%20that%20radiates%20dignity%2C%20purpose%2C%20and%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20difference%20is%20visible%20in%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20eyes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Patil.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20they%20studied%20in%20a%20space%20that%20looked%20like%20a%20cowshed.%20Now%2C%20they%20walk%20into%20these%20bright%2C%20breezy%20classrooms%20with%20pride.%20The%20environment%20itself%20inspires%20learning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20has%20already%20seen%20an%20increase%20in%20student%20enrollment.%20From%20just%20120%20students%2C%20the%20number%20has%20grown%20to%20nearly%20200%2C%20and%20continues%20to%20rise.%20%E2%80%9CParents%20who%20once%20hesitated%20to%20send%20their%20children%20now%20feel%20confident%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Patil.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stigma%20around%20rural%20government%20schools%20is%20fading.%20This%20building%20gave%20us%20that%20credibility.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T122803.296-17485019