ing%20around.%20If%20I%20noticed%20any%20yellowing%20or%20pest%2C%20only%20then%20would%20I%20take%20action%2C%20but%20by%20that%20time%2C%20the%20problem%20had%20often%20already%20spread%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Atendra%20Kumar%20Verma%2C%20a%20small-scale%20farmer%20from%20Barabanki%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20experience%20reflects%20the%20daily%20uncertainty%20faced%20by%20millions%20of%20farmers%20across%20India%2C%20until%20two%20aeronautical%20engineering%20graduates%20decided%20to%20change%20the%20script%20by%20bringing%20aerospace%20technology%20to%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20college%20drone%20experiments%20took%20root%20in%20rural%20agriculture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmandeep%20Panwar%20from%20Delhi%20and%20Rishabh%20Choudhary%20from%20Allahabad%20weren%E2%80%99t%20farmers.%20They%20weren%E2%80%99t%20even%20thinking%20about%20agriculture.%20Their%20world%20revolved%20around%20drones%2C%20circuits%2C%20and%20flight%20paths.%20As%20engineering%20students%20at%20BBDNITM%2C%20Dr%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%20Technical%20University%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20their%20days%20were%20spent%20tinkering%20in%20labs%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F319020%2Fnisha-solanki-first-agri-drone-pilot-in-haryana-gives-free-pesticide-spraying-demo-to-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflying%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20wherever%20they%20could%20find%20open%20skies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterin